Global Saltidin Picaridin amp Icaridin Market Insights
Saltidin Picaridin amp Icaridin Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Saltidin Picaridin & Icaridin Market Overview
The global Saltidin Picaridin and Icaridin market has witnessed notable growth, driven by the increasing demand for effective insect repellents. In 2023, the market was valued at approximately USD 800 million, and it is projected to reach over USD 1.2 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5%. This growth is fueled by rising awareness regarding vector-borne diseases like malaria and dengue, along with the shift toward more skin-friendly, non-toxic alternatives to DEET-based repellents. Additionally, the rising outdoor recreational activities and a preference for products with long-lasting protection contribute significantly to the market's expansion.

